description:
This 8’’ glass globe is filled with an inert gas under low pressure. The lightning bolts are produced by the Tesla coil in the middle that creates a large potential difference within the globe.   
• Comes with a detachable power supply.&nbsp;AC 12V 500mA UL Adaptor, 120V&nbsp; &nbsp;Dimensions:   
• Diameter of the globe approx. 8" (200 mm)&nbsp;

